Package: ionis-cuda
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: IONIS AI CUDA signature engine (runtime)
 GPU-accelerated WSPR signature embedding engine for the IONIS
 Ionospheric Neural Inference System. Generates float4 embeddings
 from WSPR+solar features. Fat binary supporting Ampere through
 Blackwell GPUs.

Package: ionis-cuda-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 ionis-cuda (= ${binary:Version}),
 cuda-cudart-dev-13-1
Description: IONIS AI CUDA signature engine (development files)
 Headers, static library, and CUDA source files for building against
 the IONIS CUDA signature engine. Required for CGO linking from
 ionis-apps Go binaries.
